dct_title_s: Sketch of the recent discoveries on the northern coast of America by Daptain McClintock R.N. in search of Sir John Franklin
dct_alternative_sm: Sketch of the recent discoveries on the northern coast of America by Daptain McClintock R.N. in search of Sir John Franklin.
dct_description_sm: 1 map : hand col. ; 48 x 36 cm., folded in cover 17 x 10 cm.
Includes inset map showing the probable route of the Franklin Expedition.
Shows the routes of other search expeditions and places where where relics of the Franklin Expedition have been found.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
